{"tid":2305413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[配樂] 究竟有配樂先定有剪接先？","createTime":"2020-11-29T15:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T08:49:04.000Z","uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"da1406a2e0edded6205f3c1c6c2256d1e8d43491","tid":2305413,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"以Hans Zimmer X Christopher Nolan<br />\n通常都奇幻緊湊<br />\n例如Inception/Batman/Intersteller<br />\n<br />\n睇戲嗰陣又夾得啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日劇木村搭菅野祐悟/延近輝之/服部隆之/佐藤直紀<br />\n通常都係輕快 例如 I&rsquo;m Home<br />\n又有比較嚴肅 例如 華麗一族<br />\n<br />\n成日起歌時間啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者近排既The Queen Gambit<br />\n捉期同音樂同步推進<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n究竟係配樂先定有剪接行先？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7b8a69edfb260e154a230e51b455fec27e5df3","tid":2305413,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係作晒曲先，<br />\n<br />\n然後劇組聽住首歌跟住個節奏拍戲，剪接都唔撚洗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce995f6e4f6321ea9ac5b96edef32946c55687a1","tid":2305413,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7b8a69edfb260e154a230e51b455fec27e5df3","tid":2305413,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係作晒曲先，<br />\n<br />\n然後劇組聽住首歌跟住個節奏拍戲，剪接都唔撚洗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"即係好似半澤直樹<br />\n係跟住配樂拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf959ec9b1feca0ac5688185379aa2d7db37340a","tid":2305413,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"我都係一樣選擇左音樂先 ～"},{"pid":"4423e4c8fa566a423ad9ef1ca4ba096312e9f54f","tid":2305413,"uid":117286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"兩個做法，一